name: Peace Warrior - (Studio Recording)
description:
Dear listener, This recording originally aired on Tezos Artcast @ArtcastTezos Live Broadcast August 11, 2021. Episode #021. I took the samples from the live recording and re-recorded this shortened version. I hope you enjoy it. Bright moments, Marc

Instruments: alto saxophone, gongs, Elektron Model Samples, and effects pedals.

Recorded and mixed in beautiful West Seattle.
